{
  "name": "Dominate Lab \u2014 P-CONTROL test bed",
  "description": "Mesmer has Dominate Person, Beast, and Monster (all free) + a dagger. Three foes of different types test the gating and the takeover: Dire Wolf (beast -> Dominate Beast or Monster), Bandit (humanoid -> Person or Monster), Owlbear (monstrosity -> Monster only). On a failed WIS save the target joins your side and YOU play it (radial, its own actions) \u2014 turn it on its allies! It re-saves whenever it takes damage (your own hits can free it), and snaps back if you lose concentration. Try Dominate Beast on the Bandit to see gating refuse it.",
